entry.value: SELECT a.customer_unique_id, b.order_id, c.product_id, c.price, d.review_id, d.review_score, d.review_comment_title, d.review_comment_message FROM (SELECT customer_unique_id, customer_id FROM olist.olist_customers_dataset WHERE customer_unique_id = '${'cust_no'}') as a LEFT JOIN (SELECT * FROM olist.olist_orders_dataset) as b ON a.customer_id = b.customer_id LEFT JOIN (SELECT * FROM olist.olist_orders_items_dataset) as c ON b.order_id = c.order_id LEFT JOIN (SELECT * FROM olist.olist_order_reviews_dataset) as d ON c.order_id = d.order_id;
